title: Beautiful, Spacious Home for Rent
posting_body: ['A very nice house with 2 bedrooms full bath.', 'This amazing 1,200 sq.', 'ft. home is filled with natural light and is in a great location with hardwood floors and high ceilings.', 'This home is centrally located and close to EVERYTHING..', 'Large light-filled open concept living room with multiple sunroofs', 'Tile counter tops, gas stove and dishwasher.', 'Center island and additional counter space for eating-in, food prep or studying/computer area.', 'Oversized bedroom/loft is approx.', '1067 Sq.', 'ft. with bath, closet, sunroofs and multiple large windows.', 'Remaining spacious 2 bedrooms are conveniently located on the ground floor.', 'Forced air heat.', 'Attached two-car garage located in the front of the home with laundry attachments.', 'Large backyard for yor green thumb (or not) and a solarium; a wonderful space for your potted plants, light filled and large, and may be used as an “outdoors” eating area.', 'Large corner lot with a spectacular Oak tree ready for a tire swing or bench swing to relax after work.', '$1100 per month rent', '$1100 security deposit.', 'Minimum 1 year lease.', 'Although tenant is required to have PG&E service at this house and pays electric bill, electricity usage may be subsidized by existing solar panels provided by owner free of charge !!', 'Tenant pays trash service, water, gas.', 'One Cat/ dog negotiable, may require increased security deposit and or rent.']
